    {
      "id": "59faa937-d4da-4037-8650-78ffb8ce9523",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Paper presents a system that automatically students at risk and provides personalized adaptive feedback in programming courses. Authors combine data from multiple sources to create a system that predicts whether they are at-risk or not. These predictions are generated weekly.  ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "59faa937-d4da-4037-8650-78ffb8ce9523",
        "parent": {
