      "id": "0d62778c-85d7-4b40-8c18-bdeb280f999c",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "More specifically, students under the system praised it and heavily recommended its usage by subsequent students. Also, students who accepted the personalized recommendations also performed better than their peers. ",
